President MugabeNqobile Tshili, Chronicle CorrespondentTHE Government has directed pupils from Bulawayo schools and four schools from Matabeleland South not to attend school tomorrow and Friday to pave way for the 21st February Movement preparations. The Minister of Primary and Secondary Education Lazarus Dokora issued the directive today.Permanent Secretary in the Ministry Primary and Secondary Education Dr Sylvia Utete- Masango has confirmed.More details to follow